<doc id="319645" wikidata="Q12698925" url="?curid=319645" title="Nojorid">
<text>Nojorid () is a large commune located in Bihor County, Crișana, Romania. It is composed of seven villages: Apateu (&quot;Oláhapáti&quot;), Chișirid (&quot;Kisürögd&quot;), Leș (&quot;Váradles&quot;), Livada de Bihor (&quot;Mácsapuszta&quot;), Nojorid, Păușa (&quot;Váradpósa&quot;), and Șauaieu (&quot;Biharsályi&quot;).

